[
  {
    "startTime": 0.0,
    "endTime": 3.25,
    "text": "[Music]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 6.96,
    "endTime": 7.919,
    "text": "here lies"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 7.919,
    "endTime": 10.96,
    "text": "arthur king who was and king"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 10.96,
    "endTime": 14.639,
    "text": "who will be so reads the inscription"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 14.639,
    "endTime": 17.199,
    "text": "on king arthur's gravestone in thomas"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 17.199,
    "endTime": 18.16,
    "text": "mallory's"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 18.16,
    "endTime": 21.359,
    "text": "le morte d'artur writing in the 15th"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 21.359,
    "endTime": 22.08,
    "text": "century"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 22.08,
    "endTime": 23.68,
    "text": "mallory couldn't have known how"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.68,
    "endTime": 25.599,
    "text": "prophetic this inscription would turn"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 25.599,
    "endTime": 27.119,
    "text": "out to be"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.119,
    "endTime": 29.84,
    "text": "king arthur has risen again and again in"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 29.84,
    "endTime": 31.519,
    "text": "our collective imagination"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.519,
    "endTime": 33.68,
    "text": "along with his retinue of knights"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 33.68,
    "endTime": 34.559,
    "text": "guinevere"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.559,
    "endTime": 37.68,
    "text": "the round table camelot and of course"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 37.68,
    "endTime": 40.559,
    "text": "excalibur but where do these stories"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 40.559,
    "endTime": 41.6,
    "text": "come from"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41.6,
    "endTime": 44.32,
    "text": "and is there any truth to them king"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.32,
    "endTime": 44.96,
    "text": "arthur"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.96,
    "endTime": 47.12,
    "text": "as we know him is a creation of the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 47.12,
    "endTime": 48.48,
    "text": "later middle ages"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 48.48,
    "endTime": 51.12,
    "text": "but his legend actually has its roots in"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 51.12,
    "endTime": 52.559,
    "text": "celtic poetry"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.559,
    "endTime": 55.52,
    "text": "from an earlier time the saxon invasions"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 55.52,
    "endTime": 57.28,
    "text": "of britain"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.28,
    "endTime": 60.32,
    "text": "after the romans left britain in 410"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.32,
    "endTime": 63.359,
    "text": "ce saxon invaders from what's now"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 63.359,
    "endTime": 65.84,
    "text": "germany and denmark quickly capitalized"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 65.84,
    "endTime": 67.119,
    "text": "on the vulnerability"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 67.119,
    "endTime": 69.119,
    "text": "of the abandoned territory the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.119,
    "endTime": 70.479,
    "text": "inhabitants of britain"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 70.479,
    "endTime": 72.56,
    "text": "fought fiercely against the invaders"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 72.56,
    "endTime": 75.119,
    "text": "through several centuries of turmoil"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 75.119,
    "endTime": 76.96,
    "text": "there are hardly any written records"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.96,
    "endTime": 78.96,
    "text": "from this time so it's difficult to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 78.96,
    "endTime": 81.84,
    "text": "reconstruct an accurate history"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 81.84,
    "endTime": 84.479,
    "text": "however surviving poetry from the era"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 84.479,
    "endTime": 86.32,
    "text": "gives us some clues"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.32,
    "endTime": 88.96,
    "text": "one of the poems the gododin contains"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.96,
    "endTime": 91.04,
    "text": "the very first reference to arthur"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.04,
    "endTime": 93.04,
    "text": "though arthur himself doesn't actually"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 93.04,
    "endTime": 94.24,
    "text": "appear in it"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 94.24,
    "endTime": 96.72,
    "text": "it says a different warrior named"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.72,
    "endTime": 97.84,
    "text": "guardar"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.84,
    "endTime": 100.24,
    "text": "was skilled at slaying his enemies but"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100.24,
    "endTime": 101.84,
    "text": "was no arthur"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 101.84,
    "endTime": 104.24,
    "text": "that's not much to go on but whoever"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 104.24,
    "endTime": 105.439,
    "text": "this arthur was"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 105.439,
    "endTime": 107.52,
    "text": "he must have been the gold standard of"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 107.52,
    "endTime": 108.799,
    "text": "warriors"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.799,
    "endTime": 111.439,
    "text": "whether he ruled anyone or even lived at"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 111.439,
    "endTime": 114.399,
    "text": "all is unfortunately less clear"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 114.399,
    "endTime": 116.88,
    "text": "despite this uncertainty references to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 116.88,
    "endTime": 117.439,
    "text": "arthur"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 117.439,
    "endTime": 119.2,
    "text": "caught the attention of an aspiring"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 119.2,
    "endTime": 122.079,
    "text": "historian hundreds of years later"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 122.079,
    "endTime": 125.28,
    "text": "in 1130 jeffrey of monmouth"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 125.28,
    "endTime": 129.119,
    "text": "was a lowly cleric with grand ambitions"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 129.119,
    "endTime": 131.68,
    "text": "using celtic and latin sources he spent"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 131.68,
    "endTime": 133.76,
    "text": "years creating a lengthy chronicle"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 133.76,
    "endTime": 136.0,
    "text": "titled the history of the kings of"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 136.0,
    "endTime": 137.12,
    "text": "britain"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 137.12,
    "endTime": 139.52,
    "text": "the centerpiece of this tome was king"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 139.52,
    "endTime": 141.04,
    "text": "arthur"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 141.04,
    "endTime": 143.599,
    "text": "history is a generous term for jeffrey's"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 143.599,
    "endTime": 144.8,
    "text": "account"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 144.8,
    "endTime": 147.12,
    "text": "writing 600 years after the saxon"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 147.12,
    "endTime": 149.28,
    "text": "invasions he cobbled together fragments"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 149.28,
    "endTime": 151.44,
    "text": "of myth and poetry to compensate for the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 151.44,
    "endTime": 154.4,
    "text": "almost complete lack of official records"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 154.4,
    "endTime": 156.4,
    "text": "a few of his sources contained mentions"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 156.4,
    "endTime": 158.56,
    "text": "of arthur and some others were realistic"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 158.56,
    "endTime": 160.56,
    "text": "accounts of battles and places"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 160.56,
    "endTime": 162.959,
    "text": "but many featured mythic heroes fighting"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 162.959,
    "endTime": 164.879,
    "text": "long odds with the help of magical"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 164.879,
    "endTime": 167.04,
    "text": "swords and sorcery"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 167.04,
    "endTime": 170.239,
    "text": "jeffrey blended them all a magical sword"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 170.239,
    "endTime": 171.36,
    "text": "called californ"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 171.36,
    "endTime": 173.76,
    "text": "and a roman fortress called kellyanne"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 173.76,
    "endTime": 175.68,
    "text": "appeared in his source material"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 175.68,
    "endTime": 178.56,
    "text": "so jeffrey's arthur ruled from kellyanne"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 178.56,
    "endTime": 179.44,
    "text": "and wielded"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 179.44,
    "endTime": 182.159,
    "text": "caliburnus the latin translation of"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 182.159,
    "endTime": 183.44,
    "text": "calvra"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 183.44,
    "endTime": 185.599,
    "text": "jeffrey even added a wise counsellor"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 185.599,
    "endTime": 186.64,
    "text": "named merlin"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 186.64,
    "endTime": 189.04,
    "text": "based on the celtic bard murder to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 189.04,
    "endTime": 190.72,
    "text": "arthur's story"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 190.72,
    "endTime": 192.56,
    "text": "if arthur did live he would likely have"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 192.56,
    "endTime": 194.159,
    "text": "been a military leader"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 194.159,
    "endTime": 196.64,
    "text": "but a castle-bound king better fit"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 196.64,
    "endTime": 197.76,
    "text": "jeffrey's regal"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 197.76,
    "endTime": 200.4,
    "text": "history jeffrey's chronicle got the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 200.4,
    "endTime": 202.319,
    "text": "attention he had hoped for and was soon"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 202.319,
    "endTime": 204.4,
    "text": "translated from latin into french by the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 204.4,
    "endTime": 205.44,
    "text": "poet ways"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 205.44,
    "endTime": 209.2,
    "text": "around 1155 ce wace added another"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 209.2,
    "endTime": 211.12,
    "text": "centerpiece of arthurian lore to"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 211.12,
    "endTime": 212.239,
    "text": "geoffrey's sword"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 212.239,
    "endTime": 215.68,
    "text": "castle and wizard the round table"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 215.68,
    "endTime": 217.36,
    "text": "he wrote that arthur had the table"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 217.36,
    "endTime": 219.519,
    "text": "constructed so that all the guests in"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 219.519,
    "endTime": 221.76,
    "text": "his court would be equally placed"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 221.76,
    "endTime": 223.92,
    "text": "none could boast that he had the highest"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 223.92,
    "endTime": 226.72,
    "text": "position at the table after reading"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 226.72,
    "endTime": 228.08,
    "text": "waste's translation"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 228.08,
    "endTime": 230.959,
    "text": "another french poet critian de troi"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 230.959,
    "endTime": 232.959,
    "text": "wrote a series of romances that"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 232.959,
    "endTime": 235.76,
    "text": "catapulted arthur's story to fame"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 235.76,
    "endTime": 237.76,
    "text": "he introduced tales of individual"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 237.76,
    "endTime": 239.519,
    "text": "knights like lancelot"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 239.519,
    "endTime": 242.159,
    "text": "and gawain and mixed elements of romance"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 242.159,
    "endTime": 243.76,
    "text": "in with the adventurous"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 243.76,
    "endTime": 246.08,
    "text": "he conceived arthur lancelot and"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 246.08,
    "endTime": 248.48,
    "text": "guinevere's love triangle"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 248.48,
    "endTime": 251.12,
    "text": "in addition to interpersonal intrigue he"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 251.12,
    "endTime": 251.519,
    "text": "also"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 251.519,
    "endTime": 254.36,
    "text": "introduced the holy grail"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 254.36,
    "endTime": 255.439,
    "text": "[Music]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 255.439,
    "endTime": 258.0,
    "text": "probably based his grails powers on"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 258.0,
    "endTime": 259.28,
    "text": "magical objects"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 259.28,
    "endTime": 261.919,
    "text": "in celtic mythology he lived in the"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 261.919,
    "endTime": 263.6,
    "text": "middle of the crusades"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 263.6,
    "endTime": 265.919,
    "text": "and others imposed the preoccupations of"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 265.919,
    "endTime": 266.72,
    "text": "the time"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 266.72,
    "endTime": 269.52,
    "text": "on the grail casting it as a powerful"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 269.52,
    "endTime": 270.16,
    "text": "relic"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 270.16,
    "endTime": 272.639,
    "text": "from the crucifixion numerous"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 272.639,
    "endTime": 274.24,
    "text": "adaptations in french and other"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 274.24,
    "endTime": 276.88,
    "text": "languages followed from kretian's work"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 276.88,
    "endTime": 278.479,
    "text": "in the course of these retellings"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 278.479,
    "endTime": 280.72,
    "text": "kaelian became camelot"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 280.72,
    "endTime": 283.199,
    "text": "and caliburnus was re-christened"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 283.199,
    "endTime": 284.479,
    "text": "excalibur"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 284.479,
    "endTime": 286.88,
    "text": "in the 15th century sir thomas mallory"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 286.88,
    "endTime": 288.4,
    "text": "synthesized these stories"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 288.4,
    "endTime": 291.28,
    "text": "in le mot da tour the basis of many"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 291.28,
    "endTime": 293.84,
    "text": "modern accounts of king arthur"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 293.84,
    "endTime": 296.0,
    "text": "in the thousand years since arthur first"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 296.0,
    "endTime": 297.68,
    "text": "appeared in a celtic poem"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 297.68,
    "endTime": 300.4,
    "text": "his story has transformed over and over"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 300.4,
    "endTime": 301.919,
    "text": "to reflect the concerns of his"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 301.919,
    "endTime": 302.8,
    "text": "chroniclers"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 302.8,
    "endTime": 305.039,
    "text": "and their audiences and we're still"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 305.039,
    "endTime": 308.16,
    "text": "rewriting and adapting the legend today"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 308.16,
    "endTime": 310.8,
    "text": "whether or not the man ever lived loved"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 310.8,
    "endTime": 312.32,
    "text": "reigned or adventured"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 312.32,
    "endTime": 314.479,
    "text": "it's undeniable that the character has"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 314.479,
    "endTime": 317.68,
    "text": "achieved immortality"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 317.68,
    "endTime": 320.72,
    "text": "do you enjoy sorting fact from fiction"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 320.72,
    "endTime": 323.199,
    "text": "if so you're in the right place please"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 323.199,
    "endTime": 324.8,
    "text": "subscribe to our channel"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 324.8,
    "endTime": 326.479,
    "text": "and if you'd like to help support our"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 326.479,
    "endTime": 328.8,
    "text": "mission further consider making a small"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 328.8,
    "endTime": 330.4,
    "text": "monthly contribution"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 330.4,
    "endTime": 339.5,
    "text": "on patreon.com"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 339.5,
    "endTime": 342.32,
    "text": "[Music]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 342.32,
    "endTime": 344.4,
    "text": "you"
  }
